OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1783680590
OL,3,CFire at nature reserve 'may have been
OL,4,Cstarted deliberately'
OL,6,FWatch: Video from Amy Knapton shows
OL,7,Ffirefighters dealing with the blaze.
OL,9,FA fire at a nature reserve in Poole
OL,10,F"may have been started deliberately",
OL,11,FDorset Police have said.
OL,13,FDorset and Wiltshire Fire and Rescue
OL,14,FService said the fire broke out at
OL,15,FBourne Valley Nature Reserve on Monday
OL,16,Fafternoon (6 July), affecting roughly
OL,17,Fthree hectares of land.
OL,19,FPolice are now appealing for witnesses
OL,20,Fto come forward with information.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
