OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1783680590
OL,3,CFire at nature reserve 'may have been
OL,4,Cstarted deliberately'
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Darren Stanton, of
OL,7,FDorset Police, said: "After liaison
OL,8,Fwith the fire service, we believe this
OL,9,Ffire may have been started
OL,10,Fdeliberately.
OL,12,F"I am appealing to anyone who was in
OL,13,Fthe area and may have any information
OL,14,Fto help our investigation to please
OL,15,Fcome forward.
OL,17,F"Thankfully, nobody was injured, but
OL,18,Fthese types of fires can have
OL,19,Fdevastating consequences and we will
OL,20,Finvestigate all available lines of
OL,21,Fenquiry."
OL,26,@oD@VOUtD@AOUyD@AOU}D@IO]
