OL,3,CFire at nature reserve 'may have been
OL,4,Cstarted deliberately'
OL,6,FAnyone with information is being asked
OL,7,Fto contact Dorset Police online or by
OL,8,Fcalling 101, quoting the number
OL,9,F55260101093.
OL,11,FThe fire service said it received 60
OL,12,F"999" calls alerting them to the
OL,13,Fheathland fire.
OL,15,FAt its height, roughly 50 firefighters
OL,16,Fwere at the scene including crews from
OL,17,FRedhill Park, Westbourne, Poole,
OL,18,FWimborne and Christchurch.
OL,20,FOn Tuesday morning, hotspots were
OL,21,Fbeing extinguished by firefighters.
